<!-- Container (Portfolio Section) -->
<div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64">
  <p> Red tags, like much of life, boil down to following the golden rule: Everyone likes to have a good time, but don’t let that get in the way of common courtesy. Party unto others as you would party unto yourself.</P>
  
